message.text:
Harry Ong of Munch Box Express

PTP admins with no price and pictures:

Hi OPC,

We understand the importance of tomorrow’s transport strike and why there’s a need for it. At the same time, small school businesses like ours are deeply affected whenever there are class suspensions.

For those who will still be around the FEU vicinity, we’ll be open with 20–30 tubs available. Even small orders can make a big difference for us during these trying times. 💚

Thank you so much for your continued support! 🙏✨

I’ll be on-site to personally handle the booth.

Please engage in this post so my message can send across the One Piyu Community.

You can also reserve your food just pm me.

Harry Ong of Munch Box Express
